<div id="careers">
  <h3>Careers</h3>
  <div class="black split vertical centered">
    <div class="left">
      <p>Do you have amazing skills, but feel you're undercompensated? Are you a meticulous, friendly, personable and responsible coder who works well in a team? Would you like to work remotely and still be an integral part of our projects? If you have many of the skills we need, here's your chance:</p>
